---
name: fix-bug
description: Fix a bug based on its description
disable-model-invocation: true
---

Fix the bug described in the following description, following our coding standards:

$BUG_DESCRIPTION

Steps to follow:

1. Carefully read the bug description.
2. Identify the cause of the bug and understand the expected behavior.
3. Implement a fix in the code.
4. Write tests to verify the fix and prevent regressions.
5. Create a commit with a clear message explaining the fix.
